Concerns?

portage-mod_jabber is a elog-module for Gentoo's portage to do notification 
via Jabber. You be able to send jabber notification on warnings, info messages
and errors. It utilizes xmpppy (http://xmpppy.sourceforge.net) to work with the 
XMPP-protocoll, so it is need as a dependency. 


Configuration

Edit /etc/make.conf and add the following options:
Specify jabber as the elog system: PORTAGE_ELOG_SYSTEM="jabber"
Specify the sender jabber account: PORTAGE_ELOG_JABBERFROM="sender:password@host.com[/resource]"
Specify a list of receivers:       PORTAGE_ELOG_JABBERTO="jid1@host.com jid2@host.com admin@foo.com"
